WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:09.663 --> 00:00:12.083
How do you see your transfer
to Santos FC,

00:00:12.084 --> 00:00:14.592
after playing such a good tournament
for Mogi Mirim,

00:00:14.593 --> 00:00:16.214
and during which
you scored 8 goals?

00:00:16.316 --> 00:00:21.539
I'm extremely happy
to be part of Santos FC's squad,

00:00:22.108 --> 00:00:25.012
It's a dream come true,

00:00:25.013 --> 00:00:28.242
thanks to God.

00:00:28.243 --> 00:00:31.983
I hope I am able to make
all Santos FC fans very happy.

00:00:32.264 --> 00:00:34.965
Our fans are going to
get to know you,

00:00:34.966 --> 00:00:37.615
tell us about the teams
you played for,

00:00:37.616 --> 00:00:38.929
you're 23 years old,

00:00:38.930 --> 00:00:39.930
where did you start playing,

00:00:39.931 --> 00:00:42.269
and which teams did you play for
throughout your career?

00:00:42.270 --> 00:00:44.923
I started playing for a team
from my city,

00:00:44.924 --> 00:00:46.682
Flamengo de Guarulhos,

00:00:46.683 --> 00:00:50.564
and then I played for
União São João,

00:00:50.565 --> 00:00:56.954
Santo André, Cianorte, Chapecoense,
and Mogi Mirim.

00:00:58.096 --> 00:01:04.259
Santos FC fans are going
to get to know me,

00:01:04.260 --> 00:01:08.791
and I'm sure I'll be making
them happy quite soon.

00:01:09.298 --> 00:01:12.454
You've mentioned the fact
that you are also a Santos FC fan,

00:01:12.455 --> 00:01:14.282
and now you're playing
for Santos FC,

00:01:14.283 --> 00:01:17.441
how does it work?

00:01:17.886 --> 00:01:21.067
It's true,
the penny hasn't dropped yet.

00:01:22.083 --> 00:01:26.326
I've always been a Santos FC fan,
and so has my father, my mother,

00:01:26.327 --> 00:01:27.455
my entire family.

00:01:29.039 --> 00:01:34.037
I have plenty of good memories
of myself on the stadium bleachers,

00:01:34.038 --> 00:01:35.764
a lot of them,

00:01:35.765 --> 00:01:38.911
but the penny will drop.

00:01:38.912 --> 00:01:41.932
Now I'm going to play
along with great players,

00:01:41.933 --> 00:01:43.789
such as Léo,

00:01:43.790 --> 00:01:45.344
who was an idol.

00:01:45.345 --> 00:01:47.712
I'm really excited,

00:01:47.713 --> 00:01:51.249
and I hope to be able
to correspond to all expectations.

00:01:52.879 --> 00:01:54.149
I'm really happy.

